{"tid":698400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港不會變, 也不能變的原因","createTime":"2018-06-11T15:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T17:31:54.000Z","uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef74788c8ef65a5ecaaae7b35dcad8f7c4e85c5d","tid":698400,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"香港不會變, 也不能變的原因:<br />\n<br />\n1. 狗官<br />\n2. 有樓人仕<br />\n3.地產霸權<br />\n4. 愛國廢老<br />\n5.新香港人(殖民的強國人)<br />\n6.權貴人仕及他們的親戚子女<br />\n7.在強國做生意人仕<br />\n8.有錢人仕<br />\n9.炒樓人仕<br />\n10.強國<br />\n<br />\n不要說強國了, 其實香港一大堆既得利益者, 他們有正苦幫手炒樓, 不用做有錢收<br />\n狗官又一大堆物業, 努力擦鞋將來做什麼政協<br />\n所以根本香港無得變, 也不可以變"},{"pid":"468ef7e30e421a13520a8c3cf23986d47d9c11a9","tid":698400,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:51:40.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0fa75d936f08b791de170c08a369329929e64d","tid":698400,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"根本香港一大堆自私自利, 短視既人<br />\n唔值得為他們付出什麼"},{"pid":"b84a44adf0ae5f9e183ddb1ddeb45a070e7f249e","tid":698400,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad0fa75d936f08b791de170c08a369329929e64d","tid":698400,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"根本香港一大堆自私自利, 短視既人<br />\n唔值得為他們付出什麼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"你有咩打算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc12190b3a1bb7b37c4eda249340ada37dc99fd3","tid":698400,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T16:15:28.000Z","msg":"樂觀sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf165abb64789367d